OL,6,FA care home in South Cumbria has been
OL,7,Ftrialing Artificial Intelligence (AI)
OL,8,Flamps designed to reduce falls.
OL,10,FAfter four months, they say the
OL,11,Ftechnology has reduced falls by 84 per
OL,12,Fcent.
