OL,3,CNew AI lamps helping reduce residents'
OL,4,Cfalls in care homes
OL,6,FThe lamps hang from the ceiling and
OL,7,Fhave cameras inside which monitor the
OL,8,Frooms 24/7 to ensure all residents are
OL,9,Fsafe.
OL,11,FThe cameras are linked to an app, and
OL,12,Fdetect unusual movements.
OL,14,FA message then goes through to a staff
OL,15,Fmembers' app.
OL,17,F100% of falls detected so far have
OL,18,Fbeen reached within three minutes.
