OL,3,CNew AI lamps helping reduce residents'
OL,4,Cfalls in care homes
OL,6,FFalls are a leading cause of death
OL,7,Famong seniors, and people taking part
OL,8,Fin the trial say this new tech has had
OL,9,Fa huge impact on the residents and
OL,10,Ftheir families.
OL,12,FResident Stuart Leist said: "When it
OL,13,Fwas installed, I thought it was the
OL,14,Fsafest thing that's happened.
OL,16,F"If you have a fall, it just says 'lay
OL,17,Fstill, help is coming'.
OL,19,F"I don't have to crawl everywhere and
OL,20,Ffind a button to press."
